#. ~ Description for {'str': 'enhanced bionic armor (off)'}
#: .\cbma_armors.json
msgid ""
"A tough and lightweight protective suit that combines superalloys and "
"Kevlar, this is a gem that should be called Survivor Power Armor. Power for "
"normal operation is supplied by Solar and Ratchet."
msgstr "一种结合了超级合金与凯夫拉纤维的坚固轻便防护服，堪称幸存者动力装甲的瑰宝。正常运行所需的电力由太阳能与棘轮装置提供。"

#: .\cbma_armors.json
msgid "enhanced bionic armor (on)"
msgid_plural "enhanced bionic armor (on)s"
msgstr[0] "增强型仿生护甲（开启）"

