#: .\cbma_tools.json
msgid "myomer repair tool"
msgid_plural "myomer repair tools"
msgstr[0] "肌纤维修复工具"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'myomer repair tool', 'str_pl': 'myomer repair
#. tools'}
#: .\cbma_tools.json
msgid ""
"A complete set of tools for repairing damaged myomeric fibers. In order to "
"repair, it is necessary to cancel the power supply to the myomer fiber."
msgstr "一套用于修复受损肌纤维的完整工具。为了进行修复，需要切断对肌纤维的电力供应。"

#: .\cbma_tools.json
msgid "myomer fiber (in culture)"
msgid_plural "myomer fibers (in culture)"
msgstr[0] "肌纤维（培养中）"

#. ~ Use action msg for {'str': 'myomer fiber (in culture)', 'str_pl': 'myomer
#. fibers (in culture)'}.
#: .\cbma_tools.json
msgid "It seems that the culture of myomer fibers is complete."
msgstr "肌纤维的培养似乎已完成。"

#. ~ Use action not_ready_msg for {'str': 'myomer fiber (in culture)',
#. 'str_pl': 'myomer fibers (in culture)'}.
#: .\cbma_tools.json
msgid "It does not seem to be completed yet."
msgstr "似乎尚未完成。"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'myomer fiber (in culture)', 'str_pl': 'myomer
#. fibers (in culture)'}
#: .\cbma_tools.json
msgid ""
"The core of myomer fiber is immersed in the culture solution and grown. The "
"process will be completed in one hour."
msgstr "肌纤维核心浸泡在培养液中生长。该过程将在一小时内完成。"

#: .\cbma_tools.json
msgid "myomer fiber (done)"
msgid_plural "myomer fibers (done)"
msgstr[0] "肌纤维（完成）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'myomer fiber (done)', 'str_pl': 'myomer fibers
#. (done)'}
#: .\cbma_tools.json
msgid ""
"The core of myomer fiber was soaked in culture medium and grown. It is "
"possible to take out the myomer fiber by disassembling."
msgstr "肌纤维核心已浸泡在培养基中生长。可通过拆卸取出肌纤维。"

#: .\cbma_tools.json
msgid "myomer fiber"
msgid_plural "myomer fibers"
msgstr[0] "肌纤维束"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'myomer fiber', 'str_pl': 'myomer fibers'}
#: .\cbma_tools.json
msgid ""
"A bundle of refined myomer fibers. It can be used for making and repairing."
msgstr "一束精炼的肌纤维。可用于制造和修复。"

#: .\cbma_weapons.json
msgid "monomolecular blade (part)"
msgid_plural "monomolecular blades (part)"
msgstr[0] "单分子刀刃（部件）"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'monomolecular blade (part)', 'str_pl':
#. 'monomolecular blades (part)'}
#: .\cbma_weapons.json
msgid "An extracted blade of a monomolecular blade."
msgstr "从单分子刀刃上提取出的刀片。"

#: .\cbma_weapons.json
msgid "monomolecular cutter"
msgid_plural "monomolecular cutters"
msgstr[0] "单分子切割器"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'monomolecular cutter', 'str_pl': 'monomolecular
#. cutters'}
#: .\cbma_weapons.json
msgid ""
"I have connected a simple handle to the blade of a monomolecular blade. It "
"is difficult to treat as a weapon, but it looks like it can be treated as a "
"tool."
msgstr "我给单分子刀刃的刀片连接了一个简易手柄。作为武器难以处理，但看起来可以作为工具使用。"

#: .\cbma_weapons.json
msgid "monomolecular knife"
msgid_plural "monomolecular knifes"
msgstr[0] "单分子刀"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'monomolecular knife', 'str_pl': 'monomolecular
#. knifes'}
#: .\cbma_weapons.json
msgid ""
"The handle is welded to the blade of the monomolecular blade and can be used"
" as a weapon. The connection is a bit gritty but maybe it's ok."
msgstr "手柄已焊接到单分子刀刃的刀片上，可作为武器使用。连接处有点粗糙，但或许没问题。"

#: .\cbma_weapons.json
msgid "monomolecular sword"
msgid_plural "monomolecular swords"
msgstr[0] "单分子剑"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'monomolecular sword', 'str_pl': 'monomolecular
#. swords'}
#: .\cbma_weapons.json
msgid ""
"The durability as a weapon has been greatly improved by making the whole "
"superalloy made of a monomolecular knife. If it is this, a weapon will be "
"fine even if it is stepped on by a giant zombie."
msgstr "通过将单分子刀整体制成超合金，其作为武器的耐久性已大幅提升。若是这样，即使被巨型僵尸踩踏，武器也能完好无损。"

#: .\cbma_weapons.json
msgid "monomolecular spear"
msgid_plural "monomolecular spears"
msgstr[0] "单分子矛"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'monomolecular spear', 'str_pl': 'monomolecular
#. spears'}
#: .\cbma_weapons.json
msgid ""
"A scaly weapon with a long handle attached to the blade of a monomolecular "
"knife. Even a concrete wall is likely to be pierced... not really."
msgstr "一种鳞片状武器，将长柄连接到单分子刀的刀片上。即使是混凝土墙也可能被刺穿……其实不然。"

#: .\cbma_weapons.json
msgid "Superalloy spike"
msgid_plural "Superalloy spike"
msgstr[0] "超合金尖刺"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'Superalloy spike', 'str_pl': 'Superalloy spike'}
#: .\cbma_weapons.json
msgid ""
"It is a heavy and large pile made of superalloy. There is nothing I can not "
"treat as a weapon."
msgstr "这是一根由超合金制成的沉重大型桩。没有什么不能作为武器处理的。"

#: .\cbma_weapons.json
msgid "monomolecular throwing dagger"
msgid_plural "monomolecular throwing daggers"
msgstr[0] "单分子飞刀"

#. ~ Description for {'str': 'monomolecular throwing dagger', 'str_pl':
#. 'monomolecular throwing daggers'}
#: .\cbma_weapons.json
msgid ""
"It is a small knife that is easy to throw as a monomolecular blade. It is "
"not suitable for swinging directly because it is processed to a shape and "
"weight that is easy to throw."
msgstr "这是一种易于投掷的小刀，作为单分子刀刃使用。因其加工成易于投掷的形状和重量，不适合直接挥舞。"

